<div class='commentinfo comment_'>
2005-12-22 17:09:50 (3082 days ago)
<div id='contact-11499'><span class='name'>Foster Lander</span><span class='send-message'><a href="/content/Contact/view/contactid/11499/display/detail/">Details</a></span></div> </div>
<div class='commentbox'>
As for the Ledges, I would say that the 3rd ledge (the biggest ledge) is the best playspot, but the<br/>
other holes are not bad too. I also like the sandy bottoms wave at the bottom of the rapid. </div>
</td>
